OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FThe Mayor of Salford Paul Dennett has
OL,7,Fapologised after a government report
OL,8,Ffound people needing care were 'left
OL,9,Fwaiting several years' for
OL,10,Fassessments, concerns were 'ignored',
OL,11,Fand 'human rights were not respected'.
OL,13,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,14,Frated the adult social service as
OL,15,F'inadequate' in all areas, and has
OL,16,Fdemanded the council make urgent
OL,17,Fimprovements.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
