FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FThe local authority says it is 'taking
OL,7,Fthe findings seriously' and that it
OL,8,Fhad already started taking more direct
OL,9,Fcontrol over its social care from the
OL,10,FIntegrated Care Board and its care
OL,11,Fprovider Northern Care Alliance Trust
OL,12,F(NCA).
OL,14,FThe lead for adult social care, deputy
OL,15,Fmayor John Kerry, has also been asked
OL,16,Fto step down.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
