PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mayor Paul Dennett
OL,7,Fsaid: "On behalf of the City Council I
OL,8,Fwant to apologise unreservedly to
OL,9,Fthose residents and families who have
OL,10,Fhad poor experiences of adult social
OL,11,Fcare in Salford or have had to endure
OL,12,Flong waiting times for services.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,F"This isn't the level of service and
OL,7,Fquality of provision I expect as your
OL,8,FDirectly Elected Mayor. Adult social
OL,9,Fcare arrangements in the city have
OL,10,Fsimply not been fit for purpose and my
OL,11,Fpersonal commitment to you is that we
OL,12,Fare going to fix this. We will take
OL,13,Fback control of social care, bringing
OL,14,Fthe staff and services back home
OL,15,Fsafely to the City Council, supporting
OL,16,Four residents and families to live
OL,17,Fhealthy lives."
OL,19,FA spokesperson for the NCA said it was
OL,20,F'working closely' with the local
OL,21,Fauthority to improve the service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FSalford City Mayor Paul Dennett shared
OL,7,Fhe was 'shocked' by the result, and
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's not what I expected for
OL,9,FSalford, it's not what I expected for
OL,10,Fthe town hall, and above all it's not
OL,11,Fwhat what I expected for our residents.
OL,13,F"I am deeply disappointed by the
OL,14,Freport's findings and I want to
OL,15,Freassure you that we are changing how
OL,16,Fadult social care in Salford is
OL,17,Fdelivered and we are going to fix
OL,18,Fthis."
OL,26,@pD@GOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/22
