OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FAn inspection conducted in November
OL,7,Fand published on 15 May found several
OL,8,Fmajor issues with the council's
OL,9,Fservices, which includes additional
OL,10,Fsupport for adults with learning
OL,11,Fdisabilities, elderly care,
OL,12,Foccupational therapy, and support for
OL,13,Funpaid carers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FChris Badger, CQC's chief inspector,
OL,7,Fsaid: "There needs to be more
OL,8,Fawareness of the needs of the local
OL,9,Fcommunity, so people receive the
OL,10,Fsupport they need, and inequalities
OL,11,Fare reduced. This wasn't happening,
OL,12,Fwhich was putting people at risk of
OL,13,Fharm and giving them a reduced quality
OL,14,Fof life.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
