PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,F"We have told leaders at Salford City
OL,7,FCouncil where rapid and widespread
OL,8,Fimprovement is needed. We are aware
OL,9,Fthat the authority is in the process
OL,10,Fof bringing services back under its
OL,11,Fdirect control, and we are hopeful
OL,12,Fthat this approach will help address
OL,13,Fsome of the issues we have identified,
OL,14,Fand support more consistent and
OL,15,Feffective care going forward."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/22
