CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FThe report found some people were left
OL,7,Fwaiting 'several years' for a care
OL,8,Fassessment ` a review conducted by the
OL,9,Fcouncil to identify what support a
OL,10,Fperson might need for daily living,
OL,11,Fwhich is needed to access care. This
OL,12,F'resulted in harm to people which
OL,13,Fimpacted on their physical wellbeing',
OL,14,Faccording to inspectors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FWaits for occupational therapy were
OL,7,Fparticularly long, with one carer
OL,8,Ftelling the watchdog their relative
OL,9,Fhad been 'unable to access their
OL,10,Fshower for several months due to
OL,11,Fassessment waiting times, leading to a
OL,12,Fdeterioration in their health'.
OL,14,FThe CQC also found problems with
OL,15,Fsafeguarding and had to refer four
OL,16,Fcases to the safeguarding team during
OL,17,Ftheir inspection. One of these had to
OL,18,Fbe escalated with social workers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
