FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,F"This missed concern was only
OL,7,Fidentified as a result of CQC finding
OL,8,Fit," an inspector wrote. "When we
OL,9,Fspoke with senior leaders regarding
OL,10,Fthis, they accepted that the correct
OL,11,Fsafeguarding legislative framework was
OL,12,Fnot used by either the social worker
OL,13,For the care provider involved."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@DO]pD@ZOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
