PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FThe report also found significant
OL,7,Fproblems with the way financial
OL,8,Fassessments and advice were dealt with
OL,9,Fat the council. One carer started
OL,10,Freceiving debt collection notices from
OL,11,Fthe local authority, 'causing
OL,12,Fsignificant distress'. It later
OL,13,Femerged they had not only been paying
OL,14,Fthe necessary charges, but were owed a
OL,15,Frefund by the local authority for
OL,16,Foverpaying.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FMost carers were also unaware they
OL,7,Fwere eligible for direct payments ` a
OL,8,Fone-off sum of money paid to carers to
OL,9,Fgive them time to look after their own
OL,10,Fwell-being, according to inspectors.
OL,11,FThe scheme has nationally proved vital
OL,12,Ffor supporting unpaid carers, who
OL,13,Foften are responsible for round-the-
OL,14,Fclock care for their relatives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FOverall, the watchdog found that the
OL,7,Fservice only took individual's
OL,8,Fpersonal wishes into account in 50% of
OL,9,Fall cases, leading an inspector to
OL,10,Fconclude 'people don't have their
OL,11,Fhuman rights respected' when it comes
OL,12,Fto what care decisions are made for
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,FPeople leaving hospital or care
OL,16,Ffacilities often 'felt unsafe and
OL,17,Funsupported', and services were
OL,18,F'siloed and disjointed', the report
OL,19,Fcontinued.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FA big concern raised by care-givers
OL,7,Fwas also communication, with many
OL,8,Fsharing they had pursued formal
OL,9,Fcomplaint routes just to get an answer
OL,10,Ffrom the necessary service ` and were
OL,11,Foften left dissatisfied with the reply.
OL,13,FMayor Paul Dennett said the results
OL,14,Fwere partly due to the way social care
OL,15,Fhas operated in the city over the last
OL,16,Fdecade, using a 'complex set of
OL,17,Farrangements' with Salford Royal
OL,18,FFoundation Trust initially from 2016
OL,19,Fand the Northern Care Alliance NHS
OL,20,FFoundation Trust since 2021.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FThe city was one of the trailblazers
OL,7,Ffor joining 'integrated partnerships'
OL,8,Fin 2016 ` effectively out-sourcing
OL,9,Fcare services to the NHS and local
OL,10,Fhealth providers ` and was lauded for
OL,11,Fit at the time.
OL,13,FBut the CQC's report is now viewed as
OL,14,Fa 'lesson in not following national
OL,15,Fgimmicks', according to senior members
OL,16,Fof the council.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FCouncillor Dennett said: "These
OL,7,Farrangements haven't delivered
OL,8,Fconsistently good outcomes for Salford
OL,9,Fpeople, and they have not given us the
OL,10,Fgrip and accountability that we need.
OL,12,F"This is why, in April last year well
OL,13,Fbefore this report was published, we
OL,14,Fmade the decision to bring Adult
OL,15,FSocial Care back under the direct
OL,16,Fleadership and management of the City
OL,17,FCouncil.
OL,26,@nD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FThe council said it has already
OL,7,Flaunched a process of bringing the
OL,8,Fservices back 'in-house', alongside an
OL,9,Fimprovement program and an extra #4.5m
OL,10,Finvestment into the service over the
OL,11,Fnext two years. The damning report has
OL,12,Falso resulted in a change of the
OL,13,Fguard, with deputy mayor John Merry to
OL,14,Fstep down as cabinet member for Adult
OL,15,FServices, Health and Wellbeing.
OL,17,FHe will be replaced by councillor
OL,18,FTracy Kelly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FStephen Young, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FSalford City Council added: "We are
OL,8,Falready beginning to see progress but
OL,9,Fwe need to go further and faster and
OL,10,Fwe will."
OL,12,FNCA Deputy Chief Executive- Suzanne
OL,13,FRobinson said the health trust takes
OL,14,Fthe report's findings 'very
OL,15,Fseriously', and 'recognises its
OL,16,Fresponsibility' to make improvements
OL,17,Fas Salford's care service provider.
OL,26,@oD@]OUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39620
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,FRobinson said: "The report highlights
OL,7,Fconcerns about people's experiences,
OL,8,Fincluding delays, communication and
OL,9,Fhow services work together. We
OL,10,Facknowledge that some patients,
OL,11,Fservice users and carers have not
OL,12,Freceived the standard of experience
OL,13,Fthey should reasonably expect. We are
OL,14,Fsorry for this and are committed to
OL,15,Fputting it right.
OL,26,@nD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G20/22
