OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778868675
OL,3,CSalford Mayor apologises for
OL,4,C'inadequate' adult social care services
OL,6,F"We are working closely with Salford
OL,7,FCity Council and system partners to
OL,8,Faddress the issues identified, with a
OL,9,Fclear focus on improving people's
OL,10,Fexperience of care and support and
OL,11,Fensuring any safety concerns are
OL,12,Fescalated and acted on.
OL,14,F"Services are expected to transfer
OL,15,Fback to Salford City Council later
OL,16,Fthis year. Until then, we remain
OL,17,Ffocused on driving improvements,
OL,18,Fmaintaining continuity and working
OL,19,Fcollaboratively to ensure people
OL,20,Freceive the support they need."
